name: avatar of gloom
description:
This artwork was a part of #BillelisArtComp. Competition was very inspiring. Thanks to @billelis for allowing us to mint our artwork.

Artwork was made with a combination of Zbrush, Blender and Photoshop. I've used non-realistic render technique and few photoshop tricks to achieve this look. 

size: 6700x6700 px
